    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my ride! I've absolutely loved driving this car, and it's been super reliable for me. It\u2019s in great shape and runs like a dream, though it has been loved and driven, so it\u2019s got that 'ready-for-adventure' feel we all appreciate. It's perfect for someone looking for a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready for the road. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I do!",
