    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted 1988 Porsche 944 Turbo (951), a masterclass in 50/50 weight distribution via its rear-mounted transaxle layout. This example features the M44/51 2.5L inline-four, equipped with a KKK K26 turbocharger and factory air-to-air intercooling for consistent thermal management. The drivetrain is anchored by a 5-speed manual gearbox with an optional factory limited-slip differential (LSD), ensuring optimal power delivery through corner exit. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt and water pump service to safeguard the interference head. The chassis is sharpened with M030-spec anti-roll bars and four-piston Brembo calipers over ventilated rotors, providing exceptional deceleration and pedal feel. Finished in iconic Guards Red, this 951 represents a balanced, high-performance driver\u2019s car optimized for the enthusiast who values longitudinal stability and forced-induction precision.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
