    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This vehicle has been exceptionally well-maintained and serves as a testament to responsible ownership. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, showing only minor, expected signs of use that are invisible from a few feet away. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the seats are supportive and free of significant wear, the carpets are clean, and every button and dial functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is in top form, offering a smooth, quiet ride with responsive handling and consistent braking power. It has been serviced regularly, with all fluids and filters recently checked to ensure it is ready for its next owner. This is a complete package for someone looking for a dependable, high-quality car that looks and drives beautifully.",
